            <title>[SPR-7191] &lt;mvc:annotation-driven / &gt; should supports the attributes of setting customized HttpMessageConverter bean list</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-7191</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the &amp;lt;mvc:annotation-driven / &amp;gt; doesn&apos;t allow the HttpMessageConverters be customizable (It is read-only in AnnotationDrivenBeanDefinitionParser).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is recommended to allow the MessageConverters be reference by external HttpMessageConverter beans list.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
